lign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {dy} over {dt}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 의 관계를 나타내는 선</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157305" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="4"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3310" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {dy} over {dt} &gt;0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 일 때 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157306" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="5"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 시간이 흐름에 따라 증가함을 의미. 그래프에서는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157307" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="6"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 선상에 왼쪽에서 오른쪽으로 화살표를 표시한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157308" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="7"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3310" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {dy} over {dt} &lt;0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 일 때 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157309" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="8"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>는 시간이 흐름에 따라 감소함을 의미. 그래프에서는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157564" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="109"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 선상에 오른쪽에서 왼쪽으로 화살표를 표시한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157569" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="111"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3695" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {dy} over {dt} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 인 점을 임계점(critical point), 또는 균형점(equilibrium point)이라 한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>특히 경제학에서는 이 점을 정상상태 균형(steady-state equilibrium)이라 한다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="13"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 물리, 화학 등 다른 학문에서는 정상상태(steady-state)는 안정 상태를 의미하는 것으로 쓰인다. 경제학에서의 정상상태(steady-state)는 소득, 소비, 자본이 모두 일정한 속도로 성장하는 것을 의미한다. </CHAR><FIELDBEGIN Command="http\://terms.naver.com/entry.nhn\?docId=778739&amp;mobile&amp;categoryId=520;1;0;0;" Dirty="true" Editable="false" InstId="1930157570" Property="0" Type="Hyperlink"/></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="6"><CHAR>http://terms.naver.com/entry.nhn?docId=778739&amp;mobile&amp;categoryId=520</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="13"><FIELDEND Editable="false" Property="0" Type="Hyperlink"/><CHAR> 참조.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157572" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="112"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3695" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {dy} over {dt} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 인 점에서 화살표가 모이면 해의 수렴을 의미하므로 안정상태 균형(stable equilibrium)이라 한다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157574" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="113"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3695" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {dy} over {dt} `=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 인 점에서 화살표가 모이지 않는다면 해의 발산을 의미하므로 해는 불안정 상태에 있음을 알 수 있다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>즉, 교차점에서 위상선의 기울기가 음(-)일 때 교차점은 안정적이고, 교차점에서 위상선의 기울기가 양(+)일 때 교차점은 불안정함을 알 수 있다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157593" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="119"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>y*</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>가 균형점이고 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157594" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="120"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5200" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{df(y*)} over {dy} &lt;0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ 국지적으로 안정적</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157595" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="121"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="1050" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithTe