="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>예) 미분방정식의 그래프가 (그림 1)과 같은 경우를 고려해 보자. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157566" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="110"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3235" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` {dy} over {dt} =0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 인 것은 x축을 의미하므로 x축 아래 부분에서는 우에서 좌로 화살표를 표시하고 x축 위 부분에서는 좌에서 우로 화살표를 표시한다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>                  </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CONTAINER><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1946448403" Lock="false" NumberingType="Figure" TextWrap="InFrontOfText" ZOrder="151"><SIZE Height="21610" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="35635" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="true" FlowWithText="false" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="12874" HorzRelTo="Paper" TreatAsChar="false" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="54074" VertRelTo="Paper"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0"/><CAPTION FullSize="false" Gap="850" LastWidth="35635" Side="Bottom" Width="8504"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="3" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>                                (그림 </CHAR><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Figure"><AUTONUMFORMAT Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> )</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CAPTION><SHAPECOMMENT>묶음