           </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ColumnBreak="false" PageBreak="true" ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>2. 연립미분방정식인 경우 위상도(상태변수가 2 이상)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>다음의 연립미분방정식을 고려한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"/></P><P ParaShape="15" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"><CHAR>y’</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157352" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="13"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="375" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>t</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="7"><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>= </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="7"><CHAR>A</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>(</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157353" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="10"><SIZE Height="975" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="375" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입