ect="false" Width="3595" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{dx} over {dt} `&lt;0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157397" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="83"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2570" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>x`&gt;0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>x가 0보다 큰 구간(y축의 우측)에서는 x는 시간의 증가에 따라 감소한다. 이는 (그림 a)의 y축 우측의 화살표 방향으로 표시된다. x가 감소하는 것이므로 화살표의 방향은 x축을 따라 우에서 좌로 흐르는 모양이 된다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>(ii) </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157398" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="84"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10500" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{dy} over {dt} `=2x-4y+32``=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157399" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="88"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7580" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>2x-4y+32``=`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 은 (그림 4)에서 파란선이다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157400" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="85"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3645" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{dy} over {dt} `&gt;`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157401" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="86"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7655" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>2x-4y+32``&gt;`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>이 부등식을 만족시키는 점들은 (그림 4)에서 우하 부분이다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="13"><AUTONUM Number="3" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 일례로 (0, 0)을 대입해 보면 알 수 있음. </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> 따라서 우하에서는 시간이 지남에 따라 y는 증가하고 이는 그림에서 y축을 따라 아래서 위로 증가하는 방향으로 화살표가 그려진다. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="16" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><EQUATION BaseLine="66" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157402" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="89"><SIZE Height="2250" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3645" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>{dy} over {dt} `&lt;`0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ⇒ </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157403" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="90"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7655" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION Affec