><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>두 그림을 결합하여 그리면 다음과 같다. 두 개의 직선이 이루는 부분을 4 구역으로 구분한 다음 앞에서 구한 화살표의 방향을 합치면 다음 그림과 같다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"/></P><P ParaShape="12" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="10"><CONTAINER><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1930157506" Lock="false" NumberingType="Figure" ZOrder="104"><SIZE Height="25476" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="33018" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="true" FlowWithText="false" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="22409" HorzRelTo="Paper" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="14444" VertRelTo="Paper"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="0" Right="0" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>묶음 개체입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SHAPECOMPONENT GroupLevel="0" HorzFlip="false" InstID="856415683" OriHeight="25476" OriWidth="33018" VertFlip="false" XPos="0" YPos="0"><ROTATIONINFO Angle="0" CenterX="16509" CenterY="12738"/><RENDERINGINFO><TRANSMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/><SCAMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/><ROTMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/></RENDERINGINFO></SHAPECOMPONENT><LINE EndX="27692" EndY="0" IsReverseHV="false" StartX="0" StartY="47"><DRAWINGOBJECT><SHAPECOMPONENT GroupLevel="1" HorzFlip="false" InstID="856415684" OriHeight="47" OriWidth="27692" VertFlip="false" XPos="-3807" YPos="22799"><ROTATIONINFO Angle="0" CenterX="12403" CenterY="46"/><RENDERINGINFO><TRANSMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="-3807.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="22799.00000"/><SCAMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/><ROTMATRIX E1="1.00000" E2="0.00000" E3="0.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.00000" E6="0.00000"/><SCAMATRIX E1="0.89582" E2="0.00000" E3="9185.00000" E4="0.00000" E5="1.95745" E6="-92.00000"/><ROTMA